  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The objectives of this project are:to provide physical,psychological and social monitoring to children,adolescents,women and families in a disadvantaged community in Northeast Brazil;to supply or supplement the necessary assistance that these victims need using integrated therapies with a focus on education, prevention and self-care;to educate and promote a culture of peace and attitudes based on non-violence and human rights through parades for peace and talks on self-care and access to justice</narrative>
